{
  "doc_id": "56748",
  "text": "TXNIP -/-mice (C57BL/6) were generated and were genotyped as previously reported [CITATION_1] . Akita mice were obtained from Dr. Chul-Ho Lee (KRIBB, Korea). Wild-type C57BL/6 mice were purchased from Koatech (Pyeongtaek, Korea). To make littermate control, we crossed TXNIP -/-mice with WT mice then used for the mice experiments. To determine the genotypes of every mouse in the litter, the primer sequences were used as follows: TXNIP forward ′-ATTCCCCTTCCAGGTGGA-3′, reverse 5′-TTGAAATTGGCTCTGT-3′",
